<br>
When you reach 51 get the 44/44 axe.<br>
(or the Acrylia or another good (0.9 1.0 ratio) 2Hander.<br>
<br>
After that, dont even bother with weapons again.<br>
<br>
Only willsaper+ will be on any assistance.<br>
And you wont see these before a loooong loooong time.<br>
<br>
That 44/44 axe has the same ratio as primal, and beats half<br>
of NToV 2handers.<br>
<br>
Once you get it, you will be set for weapons for a few months.<br>
